<reference id="class_audiorawdataconfig">
    <title><ph keyref="FcrAudioRawDataConfig"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc">需要回调出的音频数据配置。</ph></shortdesc>
    <refbody>
        <section id="prototype">
            <p outputclass="codeblock">
                <codeblock props="android" outputclass="language-kotlin"/>
                <codeblock props="ios mac" outputclass="language-swift"/>
                <codeblock props="windows" outputclass="language-cpp"/>
                <codeblock props="web" outputclass="language-typescript"/>
            </p>
        </section>
        <section id="parameters">
            <title><text conref="../conref/conref_api_metadata.dita#metadata/property"/></title>
            <parml>
                <plentry>
                    <pt>sampleRate</pt>
                    <pd>Int32，采样率，可设为 8000，16000，32000，44100 或 48000。默认值 48000。</pd>
                </plentry>
                <plentry>
                    <pt>samplesPerChannel</pt>
                    <pd>Int64，每次回调时每个声道的样本点个数。默认值 1024。</pd>
                </plentry>
                <plentry>
                    <pt>channels</pt>
                    <pd>Int8，单声道或双声道。默认值 1。</pd>
                </plentry>
                <plentry>
                    <pt>mode</pt>
                    <pd>对音频数据的操作权限，详见 <xref keyref="FcrMediaRawDataOperationMode"/>。默认值
                        readOnly。</pd>
                </plentry>
            </parml>
        </section>
    </refbody>
</reference>
